## The Short Version

*Full disclosure: mbuzz is our product. We've aimed to make this comparison balanced and fair.*

Both mbuzz and Dreamdata serve B2B teams, but they emphasize different capabilities. Dreamdata's standout feature is journey visualization—seeing exactly how accounts progress from first touch to closed deal across months of touchpoints. mbuzz's standout is model flexibility—7 attribution models plus custom rules at a lower price point. Neither is universally better; it depends on whether visual journeys or model transparency matters more to your team.

