| Factor | mbuzz | Dreamdata |
|--------|-------|-----------|
| Starting price | Free / $29-299/mo | Free / $750/mo |
| Attribution models | 7 + custom rules | 6 (custom on top tier only) |
| Tracking method | Server-side (SDKs) | Client-side |
| Setup time | Days | 4-8 weeks |
