## Where mbuzz Wins

### Setup Speed: Days vs Weeks

mbuzz deploys in days with server-side SDKs. Dreamdata requires 4-8 weeks of CRM integration, data pipeline configuration, and historical data processing. If you need attribution insights this week, not next quarter, this matters.

### Price: $299 vs $750 for Paid Tiers

mbuzz Pro ($299/mo, 25M records) delivers 7 attribution models and custom rules. Dreamdata Activation Starter begins at $750/mo. The price gap adds up: $5,400/year savings on entry paid tiers.

| Tier Comparison | mbuzz | Dreamdata |
|-----------------|-------|-----------|
| Free | Yes (<%= free_event_limit_display %> records) | Yes (5 seats, 2mo history) |
| Entry paid | $29/mo (Starter) | $750/mo (Activation Starter) |
| Mid-tier | $99/mo (Growth) | Custom (Attribution Advanced) |
| Top tier | $299/mo (Pro) | Custom (Activation Pro + Attribution Advanced) |

### Custom Models on All Tiers

mbuzz's rule editor is available on all plans—including free. Define attribution logic that matches your B2B buying process: weight by funnel stage, channel type, recency, or engagement depth. Dreamdata restricts custom modeling to the Attribution Advanced tier (custom pricing).

### Server-Side Accuracy

mbuzz tracks events on your server—95%+ event capture regardless of ad blockers. Dreamdata uses client-side tracking, which misses 30-40% of sessions in enterprise environments where ad blockers and browser privacy are common. For B2B where every enterprise account touch matters, this gap compounds.

### No Lock-In

mbuzz is bootstrapped—your data is yours, export anytime. Dreamdata has raised $67M (Series B), which means acquisition risk and potential platform pivots. Not a dealbreaker, but worth considering for long-term vendor selection.

## Where Dreamdata Wins

### Journey Visualization (Standout Feature)

Dreamdata's journey visualization is genuinely best-in-class. See exactly how accounts progress through touchpoints—from first anonymous visit through demo request to closed deal—across months. This visual storytelling is powerful for presenting attribution insights to leadership and understanding B2B buying patterns.

No other B2B attribution tool matches this visual depth. If journey visualization is your #1 requirement, Dreamdata is the clear choice.

### LinkedIn Audience Activation

Dreamdata doesn't just track LinkedIn—it enables audience activation, pushing segments back to LinkedIn for targeted advertising. mbuzz tracks LinkedIn attribution but doesn't offer this two-way integration.

### Deeper CRM Integrations Out of the Box

Dreamdata's 4-8 week setup time is long because it connects deeply to your CRM, data warehouse, and marketing automation. The result: richer data stitching across tools. mbuzz integrates via SDKs—faster but less deeply connected to existing B2B tools initially.

### More Established B2B Brand

Dreamdata is better known in the B2B attribution space with stronger brand recognition and a larger team for support. For enterprise procurement processes where vendor stability matters, the $67M Series B signals durability.

### Content Analytics

Dreamdata includes content performance analytics—see which blog posts, landing pages, and content assets contribute to pipeline. mbuzz tracks content touchpoints but doesn't have a dedicated content analytics layer.

